{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"81b09b5123","title":"大字报诗：组织性和良心——致林昭","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"28741d1bc8","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":25,"articleId":"81b09b5123"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"19f3f1b8ea","name":"北京大学"},{"id":"ee04913fde","name":"杜嘉蓁"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"05a125b73c","type":"title","text":"大字报诗：组织性和良心——致林昭","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"b8af265d1a","type":"authors","text":"北京大学杜嘉蓁","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"9be797ad70","type":"subtitle","text":"（杜嘉蓁：北京大学俄语系学生）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"8aa93a1fa4","type":"paragraph","text":"同志啊，不要去听","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"c2da742964","type":"paragraph","text":"那些冠冕堂皇的话语，","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"4e2039b847","type":"paragraph","text":"说：“组织性就是团员的良心”。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"1dd1279709","type":"paragraph","text":"“良心就是真理”。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"6f14c30dcd","type":"paragraph","text":"这些钢铁般的字句在他们口里，","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"47f1591277","type":"paragraph","text":"显得多么苍白无力，","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"c686448562","type":"paragraph","text":"他们玩弄着它，","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"d5c9034861","type":"paragraph","text":"像戏子玩弄着手中的刀剑，","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"c772db8658","type":"paragraph","text":"他们欣赏着它，","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"7a8a44b01a","type":"paragraph","text":"像少女欣赏着身上的舞衣。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"5dbabb697b","type":"paragraph","text":"同志啊，不要去责备","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"999f6bc979","type":"paragraph","text":"你吐露出了深心的怀疑，","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"abc9009b88","type":"paragraph","text":"我知道你为什么说出了这句话，","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"ca93aff2e2","type":"paragraph","text":"这句话含有多少酸辛，","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"ce0bf91a8d","type":"paragraph","text":"而我更清楚的知道你的心比他们","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"f51b12fcc4","type":"paragraph","text":"有着更多的真理、更多的同情。","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"97a6f09323","type":"paragraph","text":"他们“快乐的成长，并不觉得矛盾，”","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"841658ee96","type":"paragraph","text":"生活和文章都是那样四平八稳；","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"a049cf3531","type":"paragraph","text":"他们从没看见组织上的错误，","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"2e3ae9853f","type":"paragraph","text":"看见了也从不承认；","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"e0c327eb59","type":"paragraph","text":"他们从没看见别人的痛苦，","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"8145a5feee","type":"paragraph","text":"更从不感到自己应负的责任；","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"15db029b86","type":"paragraph","text":"我痛心，他们为什么","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"18e27c8e1d","type":"paragraph","text":"至今还是这样的麻木不仁","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"d7561c36c3","type":"paragraph","text":"我痛心，他们为什么","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"889ce94cd1","type":"paragraph","text":"有意无意的“为组织性昧去了良心”？","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"97f3a53c93","type":"paragraph","text":"同志啊，我知道你那","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"b6ebb6aace","type":"paragraph","text":"欲言而又不敢的苦衷，","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"acfdecbd57","type":"paragraph","text":"多少人和你一样","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"4175614762","type":"paragraph","text":"有着这种复杂的心情。","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"e0390a6071","type":"paragraph","text":"组织性——是好的！","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"406b016272","type":"paragraph","text":"如果它代表的是真理，","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"29280ae064","type":"paragraph","text":"你将会顺从它一切的命令，","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"63235eb405","type":"paragraph","text":"像顺从自己的母亲；","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"5d16cb81a4","type":"paragraph","text":"这根无形的铁炼没有丝毫强力；","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"466543a880","type":"paragraph","text":"然而，扪心自问，在过去","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"ded77c3e60","type":"paragraph","text":"我们曾多少次说出了违心的话，","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"5a7cea72df","type":"paragraph","text":"做了它驯服的奴隶，","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"6d9bd89625","type":"paragraph","text":"多少次压抑了自己，伤害了别人，","index":41,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"7893cbb9bc","type":"paragraph","text":"如今事过境迁已悔之莫及；","index":42,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"8c0aaac508","type":"paragraph","text":"有的事使我们如此羞惭、痛苦，","index":43,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"8b464ca572","type":"paragraph","text":"有的事将使我们遗恨终身。","index":44,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"abce42ea9b","type":"paragraph","text":"同志啊，如果你感到组织性和良心的矛盾，","index":45,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"2ab8a08439","type":"paragraph","text":"你要再四的思索，再四的问，","index":46,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"e6cb45d2b4","type":"paragraph","text":"别让那“组织性”掩盖了","index":47,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"678c9d7efa","type":"paragraph","text":"你的盲目、虚伪和不正，","index":48,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"82859546e4","type":"paragraph","text":"别让它隐藏了对权力的畏惧","index":49,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"7b428c7851","type":"paragraph","text":"和那些自私自利的目的，","index":50,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"e5c176600d","type":"paragraph","text":"即使在执行组织的决议时","index":51,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"cdd936dc30","type":"paragraph","text":"也要保持你说话的权利；","index":52,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"2a27e4059b","type":"paragraph","text":"让纯洁的良心抬起头来把！","index":53,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"5b8589a734","type":"paragraph","text":"即使它错了，也像孩子般无辜，","index":54,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"7d5ea6f894","type":"paragraph","text":"让它服从我们所认识的真理，","index":55,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"62b6a554a2","type":"paragraph","text":"这样，我们一定会得到","index":56,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"aeaff3a721","type":"paragraph","text":"真正的共青团员的良心，","index":57,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"1ac8e7ec6d","type":"paragraph","text":"和共青团员的组织性。","index":58,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"038b5e5664","type":"paragraph","text":" 1957．5．25","index":59,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"0945a89afa","type":"paragraph","text":"注：在五月二十二日的辩论会中，林昭同志说了一句“我感到组织性和良心有矛盾，”两天后，卫道者论坛上便出现了一首诗“致林昭同志”，作者责问她道：“青年团的组织性就是良心，团章那一条要我们为组织性昧去良心？”又问：“该怎样理解你的良心和你的真理。”作者并声称自己“并不感到矛盾。”此诗是针对那首诗写成的。","index":60,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"},{"id":"645490de26","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：北京大学社会主义思想教育委员会编印《北京大学右派分子反动言论汇集》，一九五七年十月。","index":61,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123"}],"page":{"id":"3845749b76","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81b09b5123","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}